skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Completed : cancel
Completed --> Cancelled : reject
Completed : entry / log post
Cancelled --> Shipped : cancel
Shipped --> Processing : process
Shipped : entry / log post
Processing --> Closed : cancel
Processing : entry / log post
Closed --> Processing : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml